reviewText: My daughter absolutely love, love, love the Caillou DVD!  It is played day and night.  She is mesmerized with all the storylines. This was the greatest investment! When she's happy, I am happy! Yea!!!
I like it
We love Caillou here in our house.  My 5 & 3 year olds learn so much from this program.  I love how respectful & peaceful parenting is modeled for us adults, too.  Great family show.
Very pleased, fast delivery and very nice lady handed me my package with a smile and told me to have a great day.
Great collection for the price!!

Caillou was a big hit in our family when the girls were 2~3 years old and it's a cute, clever look at toddler life.  The animation uses a limited pallet and simple lines like a child's crayons.  The stories are basic, Caillou visits friends, goes to preschool and has flights of fancy.  It's light and happy and kids enjoy it.

for parents there's not much there, but it's OK.

I think our girls (now 4) are starting to outgrow it but I still recommend it for younger kids.
